Package com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.pois.helperclasses

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeoJSON
    A GeoJSON representation.
    OSMTags
    Tags that can show up in the feature list.
    PoisCategory
    Represents a category, composed by an ID, the category name and the category group name.
    PoisLocation
    Represents a location, that have a coordinate and it's properties.
    PoisResponseOptions
    Represent the response options, which are the request values passed to make the response.
    Properties
    Represent a location's properties, which are the osmId, osmType, distance from the request point, list of categories that the location have, and OSM tags.
